This is a socketCAN driver for the PANDA Raspberry Pi CANbus Extension Board.

To use this driver copy 'sja1000_raspi.c' into '<kernelsrc>/drivers/net/can/sja1000/'
and apply the 'kernel.patch' in '<kernelsrc>'.
Run `make menuconfig` and select the 'PANDA RasPi SJA1000 driver' under
→ Networking support → CAN bus subsystem support → CAN Device Drivers → Philips/NXP SJA1000 devices
Rebuild the kernel sources and install the new kernel

Tested with kernel verison 3.12.y (https://github.com/raspberrypi/linux)
commit: 0b8e8118dd2c9440bb7a2da1a19e15e324d3c09b "Linux 3.12.25"

